de.unihd.dbs.uima.annotator.heideltime.resources

Enum Language

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Language>
      • de.unihd.dbs.uima.annotator.heideltime.resources.Language
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Language>

    public enum Language
extends java.lang.Enum<Language>
    Hardcoded Language information for use with HeidelTime/Standalone. Contains information on the resource folder name as well as the relevant treetagger parameter file and command line switch.
    Author:
    Julian Zell
